      "content": "that's a good start. can you go deeper on the part about group identity vs individual effort? like, if we aren't looking at race, doesn't it just lead to certain groups being unfairly sidelined because they don't fit the 'standard' definition of merit? i want to argue that prioritizing diversity actually lowers the overall excellence of the institution.",
